{"tid":2344241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"VIUTV仲播《東京愛情故事》係咪玩鳩木耳？？？","createTime":"2020-12-28T14:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T10:31:30.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"043624c1a253b0d9710431dc583949c17f4eec40","tid":2344241,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/05/%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E6%B0%B8%E5%B0%BE%E5%AE%8C%E6%B2%BB-%E8%B5%A4%E5%90%8D%E8%8E%89%E9%A6%99-20200504124155_2004_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F05%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%258E%2589%25E9%25A6%2599-20200504124155_2004_large.jpg&h=f6bb881a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2020/05/031608-031608-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcfcdn.she.com%2Fmedia%2Fshe.com%2F2020%2F05%2F031608-031608-1.jpg&h=e103b1f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4850/d4850537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4850%2Fd4850537.jpg&h=f59bc8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NW64YqA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNW64YqA.png&h=f2b13c83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22d3516a46035639b3f1d3e52e886a7ca4e5bdf5","tid":2344241,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"毒果啲相整到偷拍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WICL3W3B3EC72BIPS7EVIZ3SU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WICL3W3B3EC72BIPS7EVIZ3SU.jpg&h=d96e7090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6565d5f467682b85fe25b28579a2ef17fa87dff","tid":2344241,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"樓主唔跟進莫生單野？"},{"pid":"13c5182073a3800ea05ecd8ca29938e677685afd","tid":2344241,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"《東京愛的故事ー 〜After 25 years〜》<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/090571ca53f99a3c2503934032d31e62_1440w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2F090571ca53f99a3c2503934032d31e62_1440w.jpg&h=72681761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n25年後的永尾完治似乎過得併不太得意。<br />\n他當下的狀態是&ldquo;單身赴任中&rdquo;。顧名思義，指的是已婚男士單身前往異地工作。<br />\n曾經那個當幼兒園老師的關口里美，一改相夫教子的居家形象，開了一家成衣改制店，並經營得越來越紅火，無暇顧家；當年的花花公子三上也回到了家鄉，愛上了海邊孤獨垂釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；尚子與年輕的男人有了外遇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/7cdc87093592470301e6c6729062d2e4_1440w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2F80%2F7cdc87093592470301e6c6729062d2e4_1440w.jpg&h=836c7467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讀大學的女兒打電話來說要和剛交往的男朋友(莉香的兒子)結婚<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/60563fa7f6b58786255dadb65fc0a005_1440w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2F60563fa7f6b58786255dadb65fc0a005_1440w.jpg&h=a8ab1515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經營農場的莉香通過舉辦&ldquo;割稻聯誼&rdquo;為一些不擅長與異性交往的男女牽線搭橋。她說&ldquo;連老鼠都知道和異性在一起的時光有多麼快樂，而這些人類竟然不知道&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/457a6c6b420c4611c13a2b4c304b9c06_1440w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F80%2F457a6c6b420c4611c13a2b4c304b9c06_1440w.jpg&h=64837a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;想出人頭地，就奉承上司欺壓下屬，背負著貸款，忍受著擁堵的交通，對妻子感到厭倦，卻又沒有出軌的勇氣，完治你一定過的不是這樣的生活！&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.kingstone.com.tw/book/images/product/20199/2019900091627/2019900091627-04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.kingstone.com.tw%2Fbook%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2F20199%2F2019900091627%2F2019900091627-04.jpg&h=58f25377&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c83e78aca73597d74917d36e54187f7bb75ff96","tid":2344241,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6565d5f467682b85fe25b28579a2ef17fa87dff","tid":2344241,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"樓主唔跟進莫生單野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"柏洋咁由得當值律師處理算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b79ac8ce8c14c7dcddfcf7439ede34465baae2","tid":2344241,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c83e78aca73597d74917d36e54187f7bb75ff96","tid":2344241,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6565d5f467682b85fe25b28579a2ef17fa87dff","tid":2344241,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"樓主唔跟進莫生單野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"柏洋咁由得當值律師處理算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f576106d13018a225470317a7678f8425e80bff","tid":2344241,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b79ac8ce8c14c7dcddfcf7439ede34465baae2","tid":2344241